              <p>18 credits of English and other academic courses distributed as follows:</p>
<p>6-9 credits of English (ENGL) courses<br />
And<br />
9-12 credits of academic courses including<br />
Foreign language courses (0-9 credits)<br />
Academic courses (3-12 credits)</p>
    
      
      
